---
// check-inbox-mock — Chapter 053 Lesson 1, "Password sign-up", the success state.
//
// A hand-coded mock of the *whole* post-sign-up view, exactly as the section
// "The success state: check your inbox" describes it. The teaching is the
// SHAPE of this surface: no session, no dashboard, no protected content — just
// a confirmation echoing the typed address and a way to resend. The card is
// drawn calm and realistic on purpose; that calmness IS the lesson (a hardened
// sign-up is *supposed* to stop here).
//
// Elements per the lesson spec: a mail/inbox icon, a "Check your inbox"
// heading, body copy echoing `ada@acme.com` (the address threaded through
// `ok({ email })`), and a secondary "Resend email" button. The email is the
// only emphasised token — it's the bit the action carried back. A small muted
// footnote names the rate-limit that guards the resend call site (named only;
// the wiring is a later chapter).
//
// Plain HTML + CSS per the diagrams index (UI-mock shape; deliberately not a
// diagram engine). Astro-scoped <style>, no LeaderLines → survives the Figure
// lightbox, so the wrapping <Figure> stays expandable. `margin: 0` resets on
// every node defeat Starlight's injected prose margins; `not-content` on the
// root does the same. Theme-aware chrome via Starlight vars (flips light/dark);
// the mail glyph uses violet-600 — the chapter's verification-hinge colour.
---

<div class="ci not-content">
	<div class="ci-card" role="status" aria-label="Check your inbox">
		{/* mail icon — the verification mail is on its way */}
		<div class="ci-icon" aria-hidden="true">
			<svg
				viewBox="0 0 24 24"
				width="26"
				height="26"
				fill="none"
				stroke="currentColor"
				stroke-width="1.8"
				stroke-linecap="round"
				stroke-linejoin="round"
			>
				<rect x="2.5" y="4.5" width="19" height="15" rx="2.5"></rect>
				<path d="M3 6.5l9 6.5 9-6.5"></path>
			</svg>
		</div>

		<h3 class="ci-heading">Check your inbox</h3>

		<p class="ci-body">
			We sent a verification link to <span class="ci-email">ada@acme.com</span>.
			Click it to finish setting up your account.
		</p>

		<button class="ci-resend" type="button">Resend email</button>

		<p class="ci-foot">Resend is rate-limited — it can't be used to flood an inbox.</p>
	</div>
</div>

<style>
	.ci {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		margin: 0;
		font-family:
			ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
	}

	/* the card — calm, centred, recessive; the whole success surface */
	.ci-card {
		box-sizing: border-box;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 12px;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 22rem;
		padding: 28px 26px 22px;
		border-radius: 14px;
		border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5, #cbd5e1);
		background: var(--sl-color-bg-sidebar, var(--sl-color-bg, transparent));
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
		text-align: center;
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* the mail badge — violet-tinted disc, the verification-hinge colour */
	.ci-icon {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 52px;
		height: 52px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		color: #7c3aed; /* violet-600 */
		background: color-mix(in srgb, #7c3aed 12%, var(--sl-color-bg, transparent));
		margin: 0;
	}

	.ci-heading {
		font-size: 1.18rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.2;
		color: var(--sl-color-white, #1e293b);
		margin: 0;
	}

	.ci-body {
		font-size: 0.86rem;
		line-height: 1.55;
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-2, #475569);
		max-width: 19rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* the only emphasised token — the address carried back by `ok({ email })` */
	.ci-email {
		font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--sl-color-white, #1e293b);
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	/* secondary button — there is nowhere else to go from here */
	.ci-resend {
		box-sizing: border-box;
		appearance: none;
		cursor: pointer;
		margin: 4px 0 0;
		padding: 9px 18px;
		border-radius: 9px;
		border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-4, #94a3b8);
		background: var(--sl-color-bg, transparent);
		color: var(--sl-color-white, #1e293b);
		font-family: inherit;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}
	.ci-resend:hover {
		border-color: #7c3aed; /* violet-600 */
		color: #7c3aed;
	}

	.ci-foot {
		font-size: 0.66rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-3, #64748b);
		max-width: 17rem;
		margin: 2px 0 0;
	}
</style>
